{"lastModified":1764248862583,"uri":"c::7580663817::vessel::d5cc77cf-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Summer/Winter Operating Area: Caribbean Leewards, Caribbean Windwards, Caribbean Virgin Islands\n\nADEA is a 18.90m / 62ft Catamaran Luxury Yacht built in 2017 by Sunreef Yachts. Sleeping 8 guests in 4 cabins and with a crew of 3. The guest cabins comprise a cabin with a king size bed and en-suite bathroom facilities, and 3 cabins with a queen size bed and en-suite bathroom facilities.","blueprint":{"name":"ADEA","images":["/media/media::image::c::7580663817::vessel::d5cc77cf-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::2b6fdc40-a990-11ee-b7bc-d1cfb9b4dde2.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7580663817::vessel::d5cc77cf-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::2b6ecad0-a990-11ee-b7bc-d1cfb9b4dde2.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7580663817::vessel::d5cc77cf-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::2b6f8e20-a990-11ee-b7bc-d1cfb9b4dde2.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7580663817::vessel::d5cc77cf-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::2b707880-a990-11ee-b7bc-d1cfb9b4dde2.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7580663817::vessel::d5cc77cf-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::2b6b2150-a990-11ee-b7bc-d1cfb9b4dde2.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7580663817::vessel::d5cc77cf-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::4710c450-a990-11ee-b7bc-d1cfb9b4dde2.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7580663817::vessel::d5cc77cf-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::470f3db0-a990-11ee-b7bc-d1cfb9b4dde2.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7580663817::vessel::d5cc77cf-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::47113980-a990-11ee-b7bc-d1cfb9b4dde2.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7580663817::vessel::d5cc77cf-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::470fd9f0-a990-11ee-b7bc-d1cfb9b4dde2.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7580663817::vessel::d5cc77cf-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::